2016年5月12日，ABC宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="Renewed Season 2">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/05/12/the-real-oneals-renewed-at-abc-for-2016-17/|title='The Real O’Neals', 'The Catch', and 'American Crime' renewed at ABC for 2016-17|last=Welch|first=Alex|work=TV by the Numbers|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-05-12|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513062635/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/05/12/the-real-oneals-renewed-at-abc-for-2016-17/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>6月17日，《[[熟女鎮|熟女當道]]》共同開創{{link-en|凱文·畢格爾|Kevin Biegel}}與{{link-en|ABC工作室|ABC Studios}}簽署兩年新合約，並將繼續擔任本劇製作顧問。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/kevin-biegel-deal-abc-studios-1201446465/|title=Kevin Biegel Signs Deal With ABC Studios|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|date=2015-06-17|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420021404/https://deadline.com/2015/06/kevin-biegel-deal-abc-studios-1201446465/}}</ref>9月17日，{{link-en|提姆·多伊爾|Tim Doyle}}同樣與ABC工作室簽署兩年新合約，也將繼續擔任本劇製作顧問。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/tim-doyle-overall-deal-abc-studios-the-real-oneals-1201532439/|title=Tim Doyle Inks Overall Deal With ABC Studios, Joins ‘The Real O’Neals’|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|date=2015-09-17|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212161735/https://deadline.com/2015/09/tim-doyle-overall-deal-abc-studios-the-real-oneals-1201532439/}}</ref>11月4日，ABC宣布追加預訂第2季3集集數至16集。<ref name="Housewife O'Neals">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/american-housewife-full-season-order-abc-real-oneals-1201849120/|title='American Housewife' Nabs Full-Season Order At ABC; 'The Real O'Neals' Gets 3 More Episodes|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-11-04|accessdate=2016-11-05|archive-date=2016-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105161241/http://deadline.com/2016/11/american-housewife-full-season-order-abc-